      "writtenOn": "2017-11-15T01:03:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "optional: what I did in other services is setup a separate RPC server accessible only to admins and make cron call handlers there directly. That way the code is more uniform (everything is RPC handler) and admins can manually run stuff via RPC Explorer.\n\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/tokenserver/api/admin/v1/admin.proto\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/tokenserver/appengine/frontend/main.go#45\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/tokenserver/appengine/frontend/main.go#78\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/tokenserver/appengine/backend/main.go#45\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/tokenserver/appengine/backend/main.go#65",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 33,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 33,
        "endChar": 22
      },
      "revId": "0c3216a5456862ca554fc93727cfbcd08f08c6f3",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
